The paper focuses on the difficulties faced by software developers when learning about and using machine learning libraries within their systems. This falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) category, as well as the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) categories. The study also involves analyzing questions related to information retrieval (cs.IR) and deep learning (cs.DL) libraries.
